data.description: Welcome to your private residence in the heart of Pueblo West! With surrounding mountain views from this one-acre property, we invite you to tour this modern ranch-style home with elevated ceilings and open-concept floor plan. The living space is open and inviting with east-facing windows allowing for ample natural light. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, generous counter and cabinet space for storage, and counter seating for your guests! The dining area walks out to the covered patio and oversized backyard with mountain views. Off of the main living area, you'll find the owner's suite with west-facing windows and ensuite spa bath with walk-in closet. The two other bedrooms are sizable and located adjacent to the full-size bath. A full-sized basement is ready for your personal touch-- framing has been completed and there is pre-plumbing for a bathroom. Located in a prime Pueblo West location near schools and parks, with quick access to I-25, this home is ready for you
